	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為有煙火大會，<delay20 />
所以我準備了<colour id="1" />仙女棒<colour id="65535" /><delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要送給你喔！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你收下它吧。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在大型高空煙火下，施放小型煙火<delay8 />
