<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們一起盡情享受吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話是這麼說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
